title: Camp WeWow Music Week Day 3
description:
It's Music Week at Camp WeWow! Grab your pencils Campers, because today, we're writing our own song lyrics! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/activity-write-your-own-song for directions to today's activity and share what your tune with us at tinkercast.com/share! Do you know of an item that isn't considered a musical instrument but you think should be?! Tell us about it at 1-888-7WOW-WOW! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
